descript.abstract: Countries (layer) is a symbolized and labeled display presentation of the World countries (generalized) data set. The geographic and attribute data World countries (generalized) are symbolized and labeled to create the layer. All features are uniquely symbolized based on the COLORMAP attribute and scale-dependently labeled based on the CNTRY_NAME attribute.
